# Test 7: For loops (numeric range)
Show "Counting 1 to 5:".
For i from 1 to 5, do:
    Show i.
End for.

Show "Even numbers:".
For n from 2 to 10, do:
    Set remainder to n modulo 2.
    If remainder is equal to 0, then:
        Show n.
    End if.
End for.

# Countdown
Show "Countdown:".
For x from 5 to 1, do:
    Show x.
End for.
